  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Preoperative MRI with degeneration grades&lt;III at the 1st supradjacent lumbar segment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Body mass index≥40kg/m*m

          -  Severe osteoporosis

          -  Lumbar fracture

          -  Preoperative SVA&gt;4cm

          -  Spondylolisthesis grades&gt;II or spondylolytic lesion and acquired spinous process
             insufficiency in the supradjacent segment cephalad to instrumentation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
